{"tid":2222809,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"藏逾百刀具經紀被控 拘捕警揚言「我哋政治中立」","createTime":"2020-09-29T10:33:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T16:32:05.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"67ec42385a0cbeadf9e33918ce1c08233b364a70","tid":2222809,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T10:33:43.000Z","msg":"地產經紀去年8月全港三罷當晚，遭警員搜出身藏利器，及後搜屋又被發現屋內有過百把刀具。經紀被控五罪，今於觀塘裁判法院開審。拘捕被告的警員供稱，當日約晚上8時見被告形迹可疑遂截查，他形容當時光線充足像「午間」；辯方指他曾問被告「你𠵱家仇唔仇警」，警員否認，並聲言「我哋政治中立」。<br />\n<br />\n偵緝警員9751伍漢林供稱，案發當日他駐守秀茂坪警署，並擔任刑事調查隊第7隊隊員，當時因「香港發生激烈事件」，他與同袍晚上於紀律部隊宿舍附近巡查。雖然他當日便衣執勤，但有戴頭盔，身穿的風褸上亦有警察徽章。至晚上7時45分他看見被告手持黑色行李箱、揹深色背包於宿舍附近循和康徑經過，他形容當時燈光充足似午間。<br />\n<br />\n辯方盤問時質疑，案發當時為晚上7時45分，為何伍以「中午」及「有陽光」形容當時環境。伍指當時是夏天，尚未日落，所以光線充足。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200929/MLV4LGNWKZEZRP4AROHSPJKDUQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200929%2FMLV4LGNWKZEZRP4AROHSPJKDUQ%2F&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXCvUjXV925tPaxuyg6D%2B4Js%3D&h=bafbf278\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200929%2FMLV4LGNWKZEZRP4AROHSPJKDUQ%2F&h=55333df7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200929/MLV4LGNWKZEZRP4AROHSPJKDUQ/</a>"},{"pid":"8f3a99de147e622bc555b150d1bd7a6638e00064","tid":2222809,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T11:59:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e35be1fdf9e29882df37f47050203196e393eda8","tid":2222809,"uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T12:04:03.000Z","msg":"8點都仲光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eefb1c5c9baabf52f6350783eee3d50fe2f532fb","tid":2222809,"uid":8170,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T12:07:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://sunrise.maplogs.com/zh-TW/hong_kong.42.html?year=2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsunrise.maplogs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fhong_kong.42.html%3Fyear%3D2019&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXCvUjXV925tPaxuyg6D%2B4Js%3D&h=4b8c2343\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sunrise.maplogs.com/zh-TW/hong_kong.42.html?year=2019</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年 8月 1日 日落時間 07:04:41 PM<br />\n2019年 9月 1日 日落時間 06:41:15 PM<br />\n<br />\n8點你同我講似午間？"},{"pid":"3e866f1fbe503d957b69df10d808fe283745a103","tid":2222809,"uid":143499,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T12:07:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"42f2f8b602808a072c9cacef4f67490825931719","tid":2222809,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T12:11:06.000Z","msg":"大家簽左有法律效力嘅德國聯署未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「簽乜撚聯署啊？都無用嘅 不如放棄啦」<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2222912\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2222912</a>"},{"pid":"b81a7ad63506a7e53be4714f12c21acdee0f71c0","tid":2222809,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T12:11:13.000Z","msg":"案發當時為晚上7時45分<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黑狗，香港唔係西歐呀，天都黑晒啦"},{"pid":"ab4ac531f7252d0cb0228565d7fbd8dd0e4f4330","tid":2222809,"uid":168389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T12:13:15.000Z","msg":"諗起食神 叫唔好打果個 打得最落力"},{"pid":"cd31654787d31957a2f7932ce42f9d2bf1e5d187","tid":2222809,"uid":236780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T12:13:28.000Z","msg":"夜晚7點45都未日落<br />\n係咪去左平行時空